  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u15-s1",
      "text": "In 1640, a man was seriously ill.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "seriously",
        "ill"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s2",
      "text": "He had to end the last trip of his life.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "end",
        "trip"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s3",
      "text": "Back home, people asked him, \"You spent your whole life on the road.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "spent",
        "whole life",
        "road"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s4",
      "text": "Do you regret it?\"",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "regret"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s5",
      "text": "\"I walked through many fantastic places in China,\" he replied.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "walked through",
        "fantastic places"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s6",
      "text": "\"People say I'm as great as Zhang Qian and Xuanzang.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "as great as",
        "Zhang Qian",
        "Xuanzang"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s7",
      "text": "So I have no regrets at all.\"",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "no regrets"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s8",
      "text": "This man was Xu Xiake, the greatest traveller in Chinese history.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "Xu Xiake",
        "greatest traveller",
        "Chinese history"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s9",
      "text": "From an early age, Xu dreamt of visiting China's seas and mountains.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "early age",
        "dreamt of",
        "seas and mountains"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s10",
      "text": "But at the time, it was very difficult to travel far.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "difficult",
        "travel far"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s11",
      "text": "This didn't stop him, however.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "stop",
        "however"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s12",
      "text": "At 22, he set out on his life's journey.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "set out",
        "life's journey"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s13",
      "text": "He travelled for about 30 years, and achieved his dream.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "travelled",
        "30 years",
        "achieved",
        "dream"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s14",
      "text": "Xu made many geographical discoveries during his journey.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "geographical discoveries",
        "journey"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s15",
      "text": "Once, he visited Mount Huangshan.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "visited",
        "Mount Huangshan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s16",
      "text": "People then thought Tiandu Peak was higher than Lianhua Peak.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "thought",
        "Tiandu Peak",
        "higher than",
        "Lianhua Peak"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s17",
      "text": "To find out the truth, Xu climbed both peaks.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "find out",
        "truth",
        "climbed",
        "peaks"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s18",
      "text": "He discovered that Lianhua Peak gave a wider view, so it must be higher.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "discovered",
        "Lianhua Peak",
        "wider view",
        "higher"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s19",
      "text": "He was right!",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "right"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s20",
      "text": "Xu recorded his travel experiences in his diary.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "recorded",
        "travel experiences",
        "diary"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s21",
      "text": "This later became Xu Xiake's Travel Notes.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "became",
        "Xu Xiake's Travel Notes"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s22",
      "text": "Thanks to this book, we can learn about China almost 400 years ago.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "Thanks to",
        "learn about",
        "400 years ago"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u15-s23",
      "text": "\"Exploring the unexplored\" is the best description of Xu's life.",
      "paragraphId": "u15-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "Exploring the unexplored",
        "best description"
      ]
    }
  ],
